All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BaseGraph
    Maintains the graph that is represented by the underlying model.
    CircularMMLayout
    A circular layout for the OverviewGraph.
    CompartmentMMDecomposition
    This method determines a decomposition of the model based on the compartment information available in the model.
    ConcentricCirclesMMLayout
    A concentric circles layout for a SubsystemGraph.
    ForceDirectedMMLayout
    A force-directed layout for the OverviewGraph as well as a SubsystemGraph.
    GirvanMMDecomposition
    This class is an implementation of the method that has been proposed by Girvan et al.
    GridMMLayout
    A grid-layout for the OverviewGraph.
    KeggMMDecomposition
    This method uses the KEGG IDs, that have been assigned to the reactions, and the information from KEGG, which reactions belong to which pathways, to finally determine a set of KEGG pathways that are very likely to be present in the model at hand.
    LMMEAddon
    This class is required by VANTED in order to recognize the LMME Add-on.
    LMMEConstants
    This class stores the constants that are used in the remaining code.
    LMMEController
    This class controls and coordinates the actions of LMME.
    LMMESession
    This class represents a decomposition session in the LMME addon.
    LMMESubsystemViewManagement
    Manages the subsystem view during the exploration phase.
    LMMETab
    The VANTED tab for LMME.
    LMMETools
    This class provides several useful tools that may be used in the remaining code.
    LMMEViewManagement
    Manages the horizontally splitted views.
    MMDecomposition
    This class represents the decomposition of a model.
    MMDecompositionAlgorithm
    Abstract class representing a decomposition method.
    MMLayoutTools
    A collection of tools that may be used by the included layout algorithms.
    MMOverviewLayout
    Interface for a layout method for the OverviewGraph.
    MMSubsystemLayout
    Interface for a layout method for the SubsystemGraph.
    OverRepresentationAnalysis
    This class implements an over-representation analysis (ORA).
    OverviewGraph
    Maintains the generated overview graph, which models the relationships between the individual subsystems.
    ParallelLinesMMLayout
    A parallel lines layout method for a SubsystemGraph.
    PredefinedMMDecomposition
    This method is based on an existing decomposition of the model, which is contained in the underlying SBML file of the model in the form of reaction notes.
    SchusterMMDecomposition
    This method is an implementation of the method that has been proposed by Schuster et al.
    StartVantedWithLMMEAddon
    This class is required by VANTED in order to start the LMME Add-on.
    SubsystemGraph
    Maintains a subsystem graph, which is a subgraph of the BaseGraph and has been found during an MMDecomposition.
